text: Also known as [[Siku Siku]], [[Trisula]], and [[Sai]] (Okinawan). "Three Branch Iron truncheon", main weapon of [[Serak Silat]]. Originally a tree branch used to picket animals, later a weapon of the privileged classes, associated with animal ownership and metal.
title: Cabang
creator: Joshua Fontany
indonesian: branch; limb; fork; prong; offshoot; subsidiary; bough
